        "created_at": "2020-06-08T19:23:55.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thank you William - are the trellising wires as high as in her grand crus in the cote de nuits? That would be crazy, as it\u2019s expensive and time consuming to farm this way. Then again, without checking, I assume the price is as high as a grand cru from the cote de nuits, so it might work out.</p>",
